，缩放后作为高亮边框）。\n-\n-**接口设计：**\n-\n-```typescript\n-export interfa
ce UIListConfig<T> {\n-  x: number;\n-  y: number;\n-  width: number;\n-  height
: number;\n-  itemWidth: number;\n-  itemHeight: number;\n-  direction?: \'horiz
ontal\' | \'vertical\';\n-  spacing?: number;\n-  itemBackground?: string; // 如
\'bgk\'\n-}\n-\n-export class UIList<T> extends Phaser.GameObjects.Container {\n
-  setItems(items: T[], renderFn: (item: T, index: number) => UIListItem): void;
\n-  setSelectedIndex(index: number): void;\n-  getSelectedIndex(): number;\n-  
on(event: \'select\', callback: (item: T, index: number) => void): this;\n-}\n-\
n-export interface UIListItemConfig {\n-  width: number;\n-  height: number;\n- 
icon?: string;           // 左侧图标纹理\n-  iconSize?: number;       // 默认 48
\n-  title?: string;\n-  subtitle?: string;\n-  selected?: boolean;\n-  selected
Border?: string; // 如 \'quality-icon-4\'（紫色史诗边框）\n-}\n-\n-export class 
UIListItem extends Phaser.GameObjects.Container {\n-  setSelected(selected: bool
ean): void;\n-}\n-```\n-\n----\n-\n-### 4.6 UIAvatar — 头像组件\n-\n-**资源映射
：**\n-- 头像纹理：`head/{gender}/head{N}.jpeg` 或 `head/high-talent/{gender}/he
ad{N}.jpeg`。\n-- 品质边框：`quality-icon-{1~9}.png`（64×64 纯色方块，作为头像底
色/边框）。\n-\n-**接口设计：**\n-\n-```typescript\n-export interface UIAvatarCo
nfig {\n-  x: number;\n-  y: number;\n-  size?: number;           // 默认 64\n- 
texture: string;\n-  quality?: number;        // 1~9，对应 quality-icon\n-  show
Border?: boolean;    // 默认 true\n-  circular?: boolean;      // 是否圆形遮罩（
Phaser Graphics mask）\n-  depth?: number;\n-}\n-\n-export class UIAvatar extend
s Phaser.GameObjects.Container {\n-  setTexture(key: string): void;\n-  setQuali
ty(quality: number): void;\n-}\n-```\n-\n-**视觉规格：**\n-- 头像 `setDisplaySiz
e(size, size)`。\n-- 品质边框置于头像下层（`depth=-1`），`setDisplaySize(size + 
